history.proof: intros V H H0 H1. constructor. intro f. intro l. intro x. hauto lq: on depth: 3use: traverse_identifies_var.

exceptions.tactic: apply (traverse_identifies_var V H H0 H1 f l x).
exceptions.exn: In environment V : Type H : Var V H0 : Traverse V V H1 : TraverseIdentifiesVar f, l, x : nat The term "V" has type "Type" while it is expected to have type "nat -> nat -> ?V".

original: intros V H H0 H1. constructor. intro f. intro l. intro x. apply (traverse_identifies_var V H H0 H1 f l x).
